  >
    <p class='italic text-cyan-900 dark:text-cyan-300'>
      "If I have seen further [than others], it is by standing on the shoulders
      of giants" - Isaac Newton
    </p>
    <p class='responsive-text-xxs font-fira'>
      These are the tools that make my work (and life) easier 󰣐
    </p>
  </div>
</article>
